author: Associated Press
title: Wuhan’s Favorite Noodles Return in Tasty Sign Coronavirus-Crippled City Is Inching Back to Normal
description: The reappearance of Wuhan's favorite breakfast noodles is a sign that life is slowly getting back to normal in the city where the coronavirus took hold.
content:
(WUHAN, China) — The reappearance of Wuhan’s favorite breakfast noodles is a tasty sign that life is slowly getting back to normal in the Chinese city at the epicenter of the global cornavirus outbreak.
